Dunhill Holdings Plc, a subsidiary ofRothmans International PLC &lt;ROT.L> has appointed Chemical BankInternational Ltd as sole dealer for a 50 mln U.S. Dlr andsterling commercial paper program, Chemical said.    The paper will be sold in denominations of 500,000 dlrs andhave maturities of seven to 364 days. Chemical Bank (Londonbranch) will act as issuing and paying agent.    The financing is the first of its kind for the company,which makes luxury consumer products. REUTER&#3;